Class QCircleDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.lge.qcircle.template.QCircleDialog

  • public class QCircleDialog
extends java.lang.Object
    The QCircleDialog class provides a Dialog for Quick Circle.

    It cannot be instantiated by a constructor. Use QCircleDialog.Builder instead.

    Created by Yoav.
